    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not-assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. The CFD model demonstrates adequate fidelity for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied at all five operating points. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
